cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.IR. 

This paper proposes a novel embedding model for knowledge base completion, which is a task related to natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. The model also involves statistical learning and sparse attention mechanism, which are related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the task of knowledge base completion is closely related to cs.DB (Databases).
